"""
        Test that the inequality operator returns True when comparing two
        KeyWrappingSpecification structs with different wrapping methods.
        """
a = objects.KeyWrappingSpecification(wrapping_method=enums.WrappingMethod.
    ENCRYPT)
b = objects.KeyWrappingSpecification(wrapping_method=enums.WrappingMethod.
    MAC_SIGN)
self.assertTrue(a != b)
self.assertTrue(b != a)
